OL,3,CJay Cartmell: man pleads not guilty to
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of 8-year-old
OL,6,FA man has pleaded not guilty to the
OL,7,Fgross negligence manslaughter of an
OL,8,Feight-year-old boy who lost his life
OL,9,Ffollowing a firearm discharge on farm
OL,10,Fland in the Eden Valley.
OL,12,FJay Cartmell, who lived in Frizington,
OL,13,Fdied after he sustained serious head
OL,14,Finjuries in an incident on land at
OL,15,FWheatsheaf Farm, close to the village
OL,16,Fof Warcop, east of Appleby, on
OL,17,FSaturday, 28th September, 2024.
OL,19,FAllan Thursby, 64, was charged last
OL,20,Fmonth and faces one criminal charge of
OL,21,Fgross negligence manslaughter.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
